HEADWORD: Feodary
<hw>Feod"a*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An
accomplice.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Art thou a <qex>feodary</qex> for this act?</q>
